  "remarks": "Valery Tyulin is the General Director of Joint Stock Company (JSC) FNPTS NNIIRT. JSC FNPTS NNIIRT is part of the Almaz-Antey concern. 1L125 “Niobium-SV” locators, from the “Nebo” family of locators, created by JSC FNPTS NNIIRT, are used in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. JSC FNPTS NNIIRT has been developing a new radar for military air defence, which has received the current designation “Niobium-SV”. Those new radars are in service in the Russian army. Therefore, Valery Tyulin is supporting actions which undermine and threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine. He is also associated with JSC FNPTS NNIIRT.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}